DiagnosisDescription: Other ventral hernia without mention of obstruction or gangrene
Umbilical hernia without mention of obstruction or gangrene
Acute upper respiratory infections of unspecified site
Other disorders of menstruation and other abnormal bleeding from female genital tract
Abrasion or friction burn of hip thigh leg and ankle without mention of infection
Symptomatic menopausal or female climacteric states
